			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Im glad ppl are getting some use out of this guide still. I wrote this before the new SoF expansion was release, but you can use the exact same strat on the &quot;croc beach&quot; area, located in the south eastern corner of loping plains, for some really outstanding exp. 
<br />

<br />
The respawn time in that area is very fast so you will find yourself with an unlimitied supply of blue con mobs, that can all be killed via reverse charm. This spot is my new &quot;go to&quot; location when i just want to relax and grind out a lesson or a few aas for my friends and I. 
<br />

<br />
Spells drop off the crocs as well as Exquisite Marrow so loot is occasionaly a nice find.
<br />

<br />
If you have any questions or want charm strats that are specific to other locations in katta or any other zones post them here and I can help you out for sure.<br />_________________<br />&quot;Those who stand with me shall be my brothers.&quot; -Vizier
<br />
